<item>
            <title>[LU-11132] LC_BI_BDEV: configuration problem for 2.6 kernel</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11132</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;struct bio is located in linux/bio.h in 2.6 kernel serie. LC_BI_BDEV&lt;br/&gt;
uses linux/blk_types.h. That makes the configuration check to fail for those kernels&lt;br/&gt;
and breaks compiling.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
